REST API - [REpresentational State Transfer]

    • CLIENT -> SERVER
      • (http)
    • Uses HTTP Request Methods (get, post)
    • pattern for making API's
    • Example:Restaurant
      • We(client)->Kitechen (Server)
        • Waiter(API)
    • API return us the data the form of XML and JSON file
